          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "How long does SEO take to show results?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Organic SEO is a long-term investment. Most clients see meaningful ranking improvements within 3â€“6 months and significant traffic growth within 6â€“12 months. The timeline depends on your domain authority, competition, and how aggressively we build content and links. PPC delivers immediate traffic from day one."}
